text: Indulis Bikše in 2018 Indulis Bikše (born 15 September 1995) is a cross- country skier from Madona.FIS profile He started skiing at three and his father is also a skier. Indulis Bikše competed for Latvia at the 2018 Winter Olympics.Pyeongchang 2018 profile == References == Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Cross-country skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Latvian male cross-country skiers Category:Tour de Ski skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Latvia Category:People from Madona Municipality
